@danny.lan seeing `aihub-extraction` fail consistently because the Federal Exemptions field is expecting `Federal Exemptions: 20` but the reasoning field is consistently returning `The federal exemptions listed in the document are 20.`  Tagging you since you made this change recently. I think I’m going to skip this on CI for now.

Also seeing `aihub-quick-clean-refinement`  and `aihub-refinement` timing out because extraction is taking too long so will increase the timeout.

`aihub-split-classification` is consistently failing because the backend is not returning the correct page information. This seems to be somehow related to the fact that we aren’t able to load the file because i’m seeing that the doc widget isn’t loading the thumbnail either. Not sure if the above three failures are related to this as well
